---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Free Strategy Call for Therapy Practices | Moonraker"
  description="See exactly where your practice stands on Google, Maps, and AI tools. A free 30-minute strategy call with a marketing team that works only with therapy practices."
>
<main>
  <section class="lp-hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-kicker">For therapy practices</div>
        <h1>Get your practice found on <span style="color: var(--color-primary)">Google and AI.</span></h1>
        <p>Start with a free strategy call. We review how your practice shows up across Google, Maps, and AI tools like ChatGPT and Gemini, then show you exactly what is working, what is missing, and what to fix first.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary lp-cta" href="/free-strategy-call">Book Your Free Strategy Call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-video">
        <div class="video-frame">
          <iframe src="https://www.loom.com/embed/df3a5aa47f284ade81a4649695ac42dd" loading="lazy" allow="fullscreen" allowfullscreen title="What a free strategy call with Moonraker looks like"></iframe>
        </div>
        <p class="video-caption">Hear from our founder, Chris, on what the call looks like before you book.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="partners-band">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <h2 class="partners-heading">Trusted by the experts who educate therapists</h2>
      <div class="partner-row">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/psychology-business-school.webp" alt="Psychology Business School logo" width="900" height="660" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/private-practice-elevation.webp" alt="Private Practice Elevation logo" width="285" height="150" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/traveling-therapist.webp" alt="The Traveling Therapist logo" width="300" height="264" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/private-practice-academy.webp" alt="The Private Practice Academy logo" width="900" height="206" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/therasaas.webp" alt="TheraSaaS logo" width="350" height="180" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/intensive-therapy-coach.webp" alt="Intensive Therapy Coach logo" width="1000" height="565" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/prosperous-therapist.webp" alt="The Prosperous Therapist logo" width="300" height="100" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <img class="partner-logo" src="/assets/partners/mccance-method.webp" alt="The McCance Method logo" width="500" height="320" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </div>
      <div class="lp-stats">
        <div class="lp-stat"><div class="lp-stat-value">+115%</div><div class="lp-stat-label">Average visibility increase</div></div>
        <div class="lp-stat"><div class="lp-stat-value">+308%</div><div class="lp-stat-label">Top result</div></div>
      </div>
      <p class="lp-stats-note">Verified Google Search Console data from therapy practices we manage.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-wrap">
    <div class="reviews-head">
      <div class="section-label">Verified Google reviews</div>
      <h2>Therapists we work with, in their own words.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"I honestly think Moonraker is the best choice anyone could make for digital marketing. I never would have attracted the clients I have, in the volume I have, without Chris' expertise."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">BR</div><div><div class="review-name">Bambi Rattner, PsyD</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"I had no idea how much of an impact SEO could have on my business until I connected with Chris. Within just eight months my returns had already doubled."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">G</div><div><div class="review-name">George</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"The results are amazing. Clicks, impressions, and my average position have all improved significantly. People are finding me through Google more than ever before."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">AS</div><div><div class="review-name">Audrey Schoen, LMFT</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"Chris is amazing! We experienced a significant increase in traffic and inquiries through our website with his SEO knowledge. His honesty and transparency stand out."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">EE</div><div><div class="review-name">Erinn Everhart</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"If you are a therapist looking for SEO strategy and implementation, Chris and his Moonraker team know how to rank you high on Google. I highly recommend them."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">BS</div><div><div class="review-name">Brent Stutzman</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"In a very short amount of time Chris significantly improved the inbound traffic on my website. A significant chunk of the new business we have gained this past year is due to Chris and the excellent work he does at Moonraker."</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">CB</div><div><div class="review-name">Christopher Bagg</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="steps-band">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div><div class="section-label">What happens on the call</div><h2>Thirty minutes, three clear answers.</h2></div>
        <p>No pitch deck and no pressure. We look at your real visibility together and you leave knowing where you stand, whether we work together or not.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <article class="step-card"><div class="step-num">1</div><h3>See where you stand</h3><p>We walk through how your practice actually appears on Google, Maps, and AI tools, live, using your real listings and pages.</p></article>
        <article class="step-card"><div class="step-num">2</div><h3>Find the gaps</h3><p>You see exactly what is holding your visibility back: missing pages, unclear services, inconsistent listings, or a site platform working against you.</p></article>
        <article class="step-card"><div class="step-num">3</div><h3>Get a clear next step</h3><p>If we can help, we recommend the smallest of our three service steps that solves it, with a flat-rate written proposal. If we cannot, we say so.</p></article>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-cta"><a class="btn btn-primary lp-cta" href="/free-strategy-call">Book Your Free Strategy Call</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div><div class="section-label">Who you'll talk to</div><h2>Real people, therapy practices only.</h2></div>
      <p>No sales team and no call center. You talk directly with the people who run Moonraker and work with therapy practices every day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="people-grid">
      <article class="person-card">
        <img class="person-photo" src="/assets/team/chris-morin.avif" alt="Chris Morin, Founder of Moonraker" width="1080" height="1439" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <div>
          <h3>Chris Morin</h3>
          <div class="person-role">Founder. Builds your strategy with Scott.</div>
          <p>Before marketing, Chris was a massage therapist for over 15 years. That work showed him how many gifted practitioners struggle to reach the clients who need them most. Moonraker exists to close that gap: real visibility for therapists, so they can build the practice of their dreams.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="person-card">
        <img class="person-photo" src="/assets/team/scott-pope.avif" alt="Scott Pope, Director of Growth and Operations at Moonraker" width="1996" height="1789" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <div>
          <h3>Scott Pope</h3>
          <div class="person-role">Director of Growth and Operations. Leads your call.</div>
          <p>Scott works at the intersection of SEO strategy, AI adoption, and compliance, the three areas that overwhelm most practitioners but determine whether a practice grows. He writes our weekly newsletter translating Google and AI changes into plain English for busy clinicians.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div><div class="section-label">If we work together</div><h2>Three steps. Start where you are.</h2></div>
      <p>Every engagement is a flat-rate project scoped on the call. You pick the level that fits, and each step includes the one before it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ladder-stack">
      <div class="ladder-preview"><div class="ladder-num">1</div><div><h3>Visibility Audit + Fixes</h3><p>Find every gap, then fix what we can on your current website. Nothing moves.</p></div></div>
      <div class="ladder-preview"><div class="ladder-num">2</div><div><h3>Platform Upgrade</h3><p>Everything above, plus your site moved page for page onto our fast, secure Cloudflare foundation.</p></div></div>
      <div class="ladder-preview"><div class="ladder-num">3</div><div><h3>Full Practice Rebuild</h3><p>Everything above, plus a full redesign and the conversion-focused pages your practice is missing.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-wrap faq-wrap">
    <div class="section-label">Quick answers</div>
    <h2>Before you book.</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details open name="lp-faq"><summary>Is the call really free?</summary><p>Yes. The strategy call costs nothing and comes with no obligation. If we can help, you get a flat-rate written proposal afterward. No hourly billing, no long-term contracts.</p></details>
      <details name="lp-faq"><summary>Do we have to move our website?</summary><p>No. Our smallest starting step works entirely on your current platform. We only recommend a platform move when your hosting or builder is genuinely holding the site back.</p></details>
      <details name="lp-faq"><summary>Who do you work with?</summary><p>Therapy practices only: solo practitioners, group practices, and intensives or retreats. That focus is why the audit is fast and the recommendations are specific.</p></details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div><h2>See where your practice stands.</h2><p>Book a free strategy call and walk away knowing exactly what shows up, what is missing, and what to fix first.</p></div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary lp-cta" href="/free-strategy-call">Book Your Free Strategy Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.lp-hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-deep) 100%); color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); padding: clamp(2.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem) 2rem; }
.lp-hero::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 62px 62px;
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.lp-hero .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hero-inner { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem); align-items: center; }
.hero-kicker { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 800; font-size: .78rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
.lp-hero h1 { color: var(--color-on-navy); font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.6vw, 4.2rem); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
.lp-hero p { color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.75; }
.hero-cta { margin-top: 1.6rem; }
.lp-cta { font-size: 1.02rem; padding: .9rem 1.6rem; }
.hero-video { display: grid; gap: .6rem; }
.video-frame { position: relative; aspect-ratio: 16/9; border-radius: var(--r-lg); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift); background: var(--color-navy-deep); }
.video-frame iframe { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
.video-caption { font-size: .84rem; color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); text-align: center; }
.section-wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5rem) 2rem; }
.section-label { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 800; font-size: .74rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: .7rem; }
.section-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: end; }
.section-head h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.4vw, 2.8rem); }
.section-head p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; }
.reviews-head { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
.reviews-head h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.4vw, 2.8rem); }
.reviews-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
.review-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 1.4rem; display: grid; gap: .8rem; align-content: start; }
.review-stars { color: var(--color-primary); letter-spacing: .1em; }
.review-quote { color: var(--color-body); line-height: 1.65; font-size: .94rem; }
.review-author { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr; gap: .7rem; align-items: center; }
.review-avatar { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-primary); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: .85rem; }
.review-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-heading); font-size: .92rem; }
.review-meta { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--color-muted); }
.steps-band { background: var(--color-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.steps-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
.step-card { background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 1.4rem; }
.step-num { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px; display: grid; place-items: center; background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-primary); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: .9rem; }
.step-card h3 { margin-bottom: .45rem; }
.step-card p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.65; }
.steps-cta { margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center; }
.ladder-stack { border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); border-radius: var(--r-lg); overflow: hidden; background: var(--color-surface); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
.ladder-preview { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.ladder-preview:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
.ladder-num { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px; display: grid; place-items: center; background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-primary); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; }
.ladder-preview h3 { margin-bottom: .25rem; }
.ladder-preview p { font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-muted); }
.partners-band { background: var(--color-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.partners-band .section-wrap { padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); padding-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); }
.partners-heading { font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.2vw, 1.7rem); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
.partner-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
.partner-logo { height: 56px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; opacity: .85; }
.lp-stats { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); margin-top: 2.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.lp-stat { text-align: center; }
.lp-stat-value { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.6vw, 2.8rem); color: var(--color-primary); line-height: 1.1; }
.lp-stat-label { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; margin-top: .35rem; }
.lp-stats-note { text-align: center; font-size: .82rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 1rem; }
.people-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
.person-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 1.75rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 176px 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: start; }
.person-photo { width: 176px; height: 176px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 20%; border: 3px solid var(--color-primary); }
.person-card h3 { margin-bottom: .2rem; }
.person-role { font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
.person-card p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.65; }
.faq-wrap h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.faq-list { display: grid; gap: .8rem; }
details { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; }
summary { cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: var(--color-heading); font-weight: 800; }
details p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: .8rem; }
.cta-band { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-deep) 100%); color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); }
.cta-band::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 58px 58px;
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem) 2rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; }
.cta-inner h2 { color: var(--color-on-navy); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
.cta-inner p { color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); }
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .hero-inner, .section-head, .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .partner-logo { height: 44px; }
  .person-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 1.5rem; justify-items: center; text-align: center; }
  .person-photo { width: 160px; height: 160px; }
}
</style>
